{"TopicId":15524,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Amerkia - a six-engined, destructive work of flying art (REVISED)","CreatedByName":"Blitzbomber","CreatedById":16181,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-28T23:28:16Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Blitzbomber","CreatedById":16181,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-28T23:28:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EGreetings gentlekerbs,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOn this day, I announce to you the first major project from Blitz Industries! The Amerika was originally conceived as a large bomber with multiple turboprop engines for propulsion (the most aesthetically pleasing source of power, no doubt). My goal in all my aircraft is to create something that works as needed, but, more importantly, is pleasing to the eye. Other aircraft may get the job done, but this one will get it done and look sharp doing it! It could be used in conjunction with Jaanus\\\u0027 gravity bomb or JellyCubes\\\u0027 weapons pack to suit your purposes. If used with JellyCubes\\\u0027 pack, I would recommend having the missiles detach without firing so that they may fall as bombs. Without further ado, here are some pics of this amazing aircraft!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949465524439/5085203E49D704320FEC4566BCE61DF941F6EC6D/1024x640.resizedimage\u0022 alt=\u00221024x640.resizedimage\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud-2.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949465523433/4872C494C190BB78A0EC34505AC09E680A6F8F18/\u0022 alt=\u00224872C494C190BB78A0EC34505AC09E680A6F8F18\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud-2.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949465525626/B83934E04D42219C25BB978FD14A3FC42E04E9AD/\u0022 alt=\u0022B83934E04D42219C25BB978FD14A3FC42E04E9AD\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud-2.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949465522652/A1629270F3B85D79A6FC0A0E3FEB4B1DAF4127EA/\u0022 alt=\u0022A1629270F3B85D79A6FC0A0E3FEB4B1DAF4127EA\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud-2.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949465521574/C72C4CE10CE22D04277B99D3A3DC9BB04745F4B4/\u0022 alt=\u0022C72C4CE10CE22D04277B99D3A3DC9BB04745F4B4\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud-2.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949465526569/9B365436414977CF1DFA57F23F0EFE551D84BB53/\u0022 alt=\u00229B365436414977CF1DFA57F23F0EFE551D84BB53\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949465527689/2F1821AE940851F82069479D1599724C3BC078D1/1024x640.resizedimage\u0022 alt=\u00221024x640.resizedimage\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud-2.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949465528671/19C5635F7B61996DCACA981F29E218FD29664ED6/\u0022 alt=\u002219C5635F7B61996DCACA981F29E218FD29664ED6\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe mods required are, but not limited to (I may have forgotten some): Damned Aerospace, P-4 parts (for the wings), old c7 (not sure about this one), novapunch, tiberdyne, the Camera Pack and the White Monkey parts pack. If I\\\u0027ve omitted anything from this list, please let me know so I can make the necessary amendments.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI would like the community\\\u0027s feedback on this aircraft and perhaps some screenshots or recounts of your experiences with it, enjoy!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Themohawkninja","CreatedById":9628,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-28T23:33:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou made the Amerika bomber? Nice.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMaybe you can re-create other neat Nazi designs, like the HE-111, or ME-163?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tim_Barrett","CreatedById":3206,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-28T23:47:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI think it would be a bit more appealing if you shortened the front half of the plane by one fuselage and then move the wings down by half a fuselage.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Blitzbomber","CreatedById":16181,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-31T01:46:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUPDATE!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETaking into account the feedback I have received and looking back at some prototype photos, I have come up with some alterations which improve the look of this aircraft tenfold. The wings have been slimmed down slightly, their shape modified; the tail section has been redone; the fuselage shortened slightly; and ASAS has been added. The aircraft does tend to nose up a bit but I hope to have this remedied shortly. In the meantime, enjoy these pictures and an updated craft file!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud-2.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949495503869/72EF6B1189E8EC4F791713314551E6CD1E835171/1024x640.resizedimage\u0022 alt=\u00221024x640.resizedimage\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949495505712/677E66B276DE99E8EBFDC6A7B6D76511E8E10AB3/1024x640.resizedimage\u0022 alt=\u00221024x640.resizedimage\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud-2.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949495504809/4A2F37CE18266A8BB6C6A7620A8BC4B285AF29B2/1024x640.resizedimage\u0022 alt=\u00221024x640.resizedimage\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949495504364/0E7F9C6C59C1809220FAEAC8C10D7F2C680F3728/1024x640.resizedimage\u0022 alt=\u00221024x640.resizedimage\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949495506607/7FCC24E053B20DFCD82BE89390BB57FCE9A5587D/1024x640.resizedimage\u0022 alt=\u00221024x640.resizedimage\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud.steampowered.com/ugc/576710949495507066/610ED8E835C3725A04175B47586B8F5C262239A1/1024x640.resizedimage\u0022 alt=\u00221024x640.resizedimage\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECriticism always appreciated, enjoy!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Phoenix Aerospace","CreatedById":26120,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-31T02:13:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHow\\\u0027s the range on that sucker? Can it do a round-trip to the next continent? More? I\\\u0027m curious.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Cobbler","CreatedById":30259,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-31T02:28:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ecan i use this in the rp forums?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tim_Barrett","CreatedById":3206,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-31T03:08:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Blitzbomber\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Blitzbomber\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUPDATE!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\\\u0027m glad you took my advice; looks so awesome now! \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGood job! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"samstarman5","CreatedById":12469,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-31T10:02:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHow\\\u0027s the range on that sucker? Can it do a round-trip to the next continent? More? I\\\u0027m curious.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAs long as it reaches the corner 7-11, I\\\u0027m happy.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Blitzbomber","CreatedById":16181,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-31T21:22:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHow\\\u0027s the range on that sucker? Can it do a round-trip to the next continent? More? I\\\u0027m curious.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt has a really long range and could easily make it to the next continent if I had the patience to do so.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tim_Barrett\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Tim_Barrett\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\\\u0027m glad you took my advice; looks so awesome now! \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGood job! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGlad you like it, it made all the difference!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ecan i use this in the rp forums?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI suppose so, if you credit and link me to whatever it is you\\\u0027re doing!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHas anyone operated it yet, I\\\u0027m anxious to get your thoughts on it! Perhaps I should make a combat-ready version?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Cobbler","CreatedById":30259,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-08-01T02:13:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThank you, you will be credited\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"A_Tea_Heist","CreatedById":35733,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-08-01T16:31:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EVery well done sir. Playing around with it now, loads of fun.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}